~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : review                                    ~FTRNUTS Version 3.0.2
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : review [<roomname>]

   This will show the last few lines of conversation, emoting and 
   echoes that took place in the room which you are in.  If you have 
   gate crash or are a wiz then you can review rooms that you are not 
   currently in.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : revtell, revshout
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
